South African hair line brand, Precious Brand Hair Couture has opened a new branch in Capetown at Ronderbosh main shopping centre, South Africa. According to the founder, Precious Udoye fondly called ‘The Boss lady ‘ on her Instagram page, it is the sixth hair line store the company would be opening in South Africa   STEM learning will build Africa beyond aid – GetBundi…     US welcomes ECOWAS agreement on transition in Mali     Paramount Africa examines on-screen diversity to improve…   “Thanks to everyone who has been supporting and demanding for a store in Capetown. We listened and see that as a nice idea to satisfy our customers’ needs. We have opened a store for you and sales are available,” she said. Precious Udoye is the founder of Precious Brand Hair Couture and a celebrity hair artist who has been empowering youths with her creativity.